Product Catalog Management

Use Dynamic Options to Add All Products Based On a Product Classification to a Product Bundle.

Your product designers can now dynamically add all optional products with similar characteristics to a configurable product bundle, even as the product components in the bundle grow and evolve over time. 

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.
